  ('q-c3c-w2', 'prod-cert3-community', 'ver-cert3-community-v1', 'Document a client''s behavioral changes including triggers, interventions attempted, and outcomes.', 'short_answer', null, 'Writing', 6, 'Client became agitated at 3pm (trigger: loud noise from construction). Interventions: moved to quiet room, offered preferred activity, used calm voice. Outcome: Settled within 20 minutes, participated in activity.', 1.0, 'Document a client''s behavioral changes including triggers, interventions attempted, and outcomes.', 'short_answer', 'Writing', 'Client became agitated at 3pm (trigger: loud noise from construction). Interventions: moved to quiet room, offered preferred activity, used calm voice. Outcome: Settled within 20 minutes, participated in activity.', 1.0, 'Writes behavioral observations', 3),
