  ('q-c4c-r1', 'prod-cert4-community', 'ver-cert4-community-v1', 'Critically analyse this policy on restraint use. Identify potential ethical and legal issues.', 'short_answer', null, 'Reading', 1, 'Policy lacks informed consent procedures, doesn''t specify least restrictive options, missing review timeframes. Legal risks include human rights violations and duty of care breaches.', 1.0, 'Critically analyse this policy on restraint use. Identify potential ethical and legal issues.', 'short_answer', 'Reading', 'Policy lacks informed consent procedures, doesn''t specify least restrictive options, missing review timeframes. Legal risks include human rights violations and duty of care breaches.', 1.0, 'Critically analyses policy', 4),
